---
title: Dukkah-Roasted Chicken with Sweet Potatoes, Snap Peas, and Citrus Sour Cream
description: We’ve fallen in love with dukkah—an Egyptian spice blend containing crushed nuts, sesame seeds, cumin, and coriander. It’s earthy and nutty in all the best ways. It gives this simple, pan-seared chicken and roasted sweet potatoes a major upgrade!
